POST {{baseUrl}}/products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{authToken}}

{
  "name": "Malt 35cl",
  "sku_code": "MLT-035",
  "cost_price": 5200
}

### Create second Product
POST {{baseUrl}}/products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{authToken}}

{
  "name": "Malt 50cl",
  "sku_code": "MLT-050",
  "cost_price": 5500
}

### Create third Product
POST {{baseUrl}}/products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{authToken}}

{
  "name": "Energy Drink 25cl",
  "sku_code": "EDR-025",
  "cost_price": 3200
}

### Get specific Product (replace with actual ID)
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/{{productId}}
